  "text": "The cDNA AalbOPB46 (GenBank accession no. FJ040863) is 1,064 bp in length, with a 61-bp 5Ј UTR and a 106-bp 3Ј UTR with a poly-A tail. The open reading frame is 897 bp and encodes a 298 amino acid protein with a predicted mass of 31.1 kDa and a 21-bp signal peptide. The BLASTP results of the inferred open reading frame from ORF Finder indicated the closest match to this Ae. albopictus sequence is a hy- [CITATION_1] ) that matches with an E-value ϭ 10 Ϫ83 and 57% identity.",
